If you came from reddit, you can comment
there. You can also create an Issue on
the GitHub page,
https://github.com/GageSorrell/de_alien/)
Description : A secret U.S. research facility has been
uncovered to the public and has been oper-
ating on captured alien subjects. A terr-
orist group has broken into the facility
in an attempt to free aliens.
Basic Information
Thank you for trying out my map.
de_alien is my first map, I hope to make a map that
people enjoy, and makes their lives better by providing
fun gameplay. I believe that leisure is an important
part of a balanced, healthy life, and I hope I can make
your lives better through my work.
Feel free to send feedback via email or GitHub, or via
comment on reddit if it was my post (that way I will see
them, I am u/Gage_Sorrell). Helpful feedback to me can
be "Lots of fun, thanks!", a 3kliks-esque editorial, or
anywhere in-between.
If I am lucky enough for you to make a video with my map
in it, please send me a link of the video (but of course
this isn't a requirement).
Enjoy and thank you!
An Open Letter
